      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦对市场降息观点表示满意</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-more-cuts-before-rates-no-longer-restrictive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行将在 2025 年进一步降低借贷成本，投资者对降息超过 100 个基点的押注看起来是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-more-cuts-before-rates-no-longer-restrictive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济萎缩使工党的增长承诺面临新的质疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/uk-economy-unexpectedly-shrinks-at-start-of-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者面临痛苦的预算压力，英国经济十月份连续第二个月萎缩，使得工党政府执政仅数月的促进经济增长的承诺陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/uk-economy-unexpectedly-shrinks-at-start-of-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
